name: 2022 6th International Conference on Computational Biology and Bioinformatics
content: Paper Publishing and Indexing: ICCBB 2022 papers will be published in the ACM Internatinal Conference Proceedings (ISBN: 978-1-4503-9764-3), which will be archived in ACM Digital Library, indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus, and submitted to be reviewed by CPCI.
